nodes.text: The Muskeg Reactionaries Camp was a ruined building located in the Lasay Swamp of the world of Naboo. Following the Battle of Yavin, the building was used as a camp by the Muskegs, a fanatical and violent sect of Gungans. Circa 1 ABY, Boss Rugor Nass sent a spacer to the camp in order to retrieve a valuable Gungan artifact stolen by Flossin Noz, a Muskeg zealot chief. Several Muskeg reactionaries were killed during the assault.
